====Woodland Hills====
Universal Music Group operates a secondary office in Woodland Hills that includes finance, royalty, and operations functions.<ref>{{cite magazine |last1=Levine |first1=Robert |title=Cindy Oliver Q&A: Getting to Know the EVP in Charge of Doling Out the Dough to Universal Music Artists |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/8466345/cindy-oliver-universal-music-royalty-revenue-interview |magazine=Billboard |access-date=May 30, 2019 |archive-date=June 8, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608010534/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/8466345/cindy-oliver-universal-music-royalty-revenue-interview |url-status=live }}</ref>

